- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper discusses algorithms for PCA. 
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is relevant as the paper discusses the accuracy of the output and the trade-off between communication cost and accuracy. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as PCA is commonly used in multimedia applications such as image and video processing.
